    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "#FFFFFF"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>检查与修复</strong></p>

  - elementId: step-6-badge
    elementType: text
    bounds: [420, 525, 130, 35]
    content:
      fontSize: 13
      color: "#4A5CFF"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>→ checker</p>

  # 箭头 6→7
  - elementId: arrow-6
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [225, 570, 0, 25]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    arrow: [null, "arrow"]
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 2
      color: "#4A5CFF"

  # Step 7
  - elementId: step-7-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 595, 350, 55]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 2
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: step-7-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [70, 595, 70, 55]
    content:
      fontSize: 28
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>07</strong></p>

  - elementId: step-7-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [140, 595, 260, 55]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>交付 .pptd 文件</strong></p>

  # 右侧说明区域
  - elementId: right-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [580, 115, 400, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      letterSpacing: 3
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>WORKFLOW DETAILS</p>

  # 说明卡片 1
  - elementId: detail-1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [580, 150, 640, 110]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"

  - elementId: detail-1-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [580, 150, 4, 110]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: detail-1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 158, 300, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Step 1-2：分析阶段</strong></p>

  - elementId: detail-1-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 190, 600, 55]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>分析语言需求、参考材料、页数要求、内容要求、视觉要求、目标受众</p>
        <p>确定内容模式（Summary/Outline/Search）和视觉模式（Creative/Reference/Template）</p>

  # 说明卡片 2
  - elementId: detail-2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [580, 275, 640, 110]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"

  - elementId: detail-2-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [580, 275, 4, 110]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: detail-2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 283, 300, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Step 3-4：设计阶段</strong></p>

  - elementId: detail-2-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 315, 600, 55]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>视觉设计 → 产出 design.md（风格、色彩、字体、布局、主题定义）</p>
        <p>内容设计 → 产出 outline.md（每页标题、要点、内容规划）</p>

  # 说明卡片 3
  - elementId: detail-3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [580, 400, 640, 110]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"

  - elementId: detail-3-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [580, 400, 4, 110]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "#4A5CFF"

  - elementId: detail-3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 408, 300, 26]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter, alimamashuheiti"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Step 5-7：构建阶段</strong></p>

  - elementId: detail-3-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [600, 440, 600, 55]
    content:
      fontSize: 14
      color: "$secondary"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>生成 .pptd 主入口文件 → 创建 .page 页面文件（子代理执行）</p>
        <p>运行 check.sh 检查 → 修复问题 → 交付 .pptd 文件</p>

  # 页码
  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1170, 680, 60, 20]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>11</p>